item.title: Double room
item.dc:creator: vamtam
item.content:encoded:
Escape to New York with the Manhattan Retreat package, offering great value plus a number of added benefits tailored for the perfect urban getaway. With room rates from US$ 145 per night, the Manhattan Retreat Package includes benefits such as daily Continental breakfast, spa discount, late check out and more at a savings of more than 30 percent.

PACKAGE BENEFITS:

  • 30% off treatments atÂ The Peninsula Spa
  • Daily Continental breakfast for two adults Bottle of red wine
  • Guaranteed 4:00 pm late check-out

STANDARD COMPLIMENTARY BENEFITS:

  • Wired and wireless hi-speed Internet
  • Local and international phone calls
  • Daily local newspaper

ROOM RATES:

  • From US$ 145

RESTRICTIONS:

  • Minimum stay of two consecutive nights
Terms & Conditions:
  • The rate is subject to availability and black-out dates may apply
  • The rates are subject to 14.75% tax and $3.50 occupancy tax per room per night based on single or double occupancy
  • Advance reservations are required
  • This offer cannot be used in conjunction with any other offers, programmes and/or promotions and is not valid for groups
  • In case of any dispute, the hotel reserves the right to make the final decision
